title: Gordon Ramsay cooks up a meal in London Zoo | The F Word With Foxy Games
description:
.
Season 4 of 6 of The F Word with Gordon Ramsay and celebrity cooking brigades.

Gordon goes to London Zoo to help Hannah, a zookeeper with gluten and dairy intolerance, cook great tasting food: pan roasted fillet of (organic) beef with tomato and tarragon dressing and poppy seed, parsley and celeriac coleslaw.  .
